  <span id="freeText11483155109769299958" style="display:none">Some of the poems in this book are really fine, and some made me go "meh." The sequences, for the most part, engaged me the most. Strand is a better poet than this collection, as a whole, demonstrates. However, the volume is worth reading.</span>
